<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>In many projects it's really comfortable to use sequences (for example in creating new DB related objects). Unfortunately some DBs like MySQL use autoincrement instead. In some projects like PEAR: DB and MDB2 for these databases sequence emulator was written. It would be great see the same in Zend's DB adapters.</p>

